Package: OpenCL
Version: 0.2-11
Title: Interface allowing R to use OpenCL
Author: Simon Urbanek [aut, cre, cph] (https://urbanek.nz, ORCID: <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2297-1732>), Aaron Puchert [aut]
Authors@R: c(person("Simon", "Urbanek", role=c("aut","cre","cph"), email="Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org", comment=c("https://urbanek.nz", ORCID="0000-0003-2297-1732")), person("Aaron", "Puchert", role="aut", email="aaronpuchert@alice-dsl.net"))
Maintainer: Simon Urbanek <Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org>
Depends: R (>= 2.0.0)
Description: This package provides an interface to OpenCL, allowing R to leverage computing power of GPUs and other HPC accelerator devices.
